	(text "LAN8710 is not the cheapest, but it's cheap enough,\nand it's already in kicad, so one less thing to fuck with.\nWe can't use 83825i, because it's rmii ONLY\n\nRTL8201 / SR8201 would be _cheaper_ but, youd need ot make the kicad symbols first, and not meaningful dollars"
